Innal-Hamdu lillah was-Salaatu was-Salaam `alaa Rasoolillah
&ldquo;Lucky escape &hellip; hmmm &hellip; Nah! It just wasn&rsquo;t my time to go yet; Allah saved me and gave me a little longer &hellip;&rdquo;
Driving home from work after having a late staff meeting, it was an ordinary evening not much traffic on the road. I got onto the dual carriage, I was in the right lane doing around 60-70 miles an hour, then all of a sudden *BANG* the bonnet of my car flew open and smashed against my car windscreen, *SMASH* all the glass cracked and from the great impact, my back view mirror had completely broken off.
